    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Discretization error achieved Level 3 against a Level 2 requirement, providing additional confidence margin. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the specified COU.",
